The project can be automated to run on any CI/CD tools like Jenkins, Bamboo etc.

Steps for Jenkins integration:

1) Install jenkins on a machine
2) Once installation is done,
    navigate to the Jenkins Dashboard in the browser window and
    Click on the New Item link to create a CI job.

3)Select as maven project and configure the system like JDK
4) Give the location of pom file and add the command clean test
5) Schedule it to run periodically and set up the email notification

Cheers.

